information: Worldplas specializes in designing and manufacturing technical thermoplastic parts for all industrial sectors: aeronautics, medical, automotive, luxury, etc. We undertake injection moulding of all thermoplastics for technical and decorative parts, from the prototype to mass production. Worldplas develops thermoplastic sets and sub-sets and comprehensive, global solutions that call on its thermoplastic injection moulding, overmoulding, stamping, assembly and careful finishing skills. Thanks to its leading-edge facilities and strict organization, Worldplas can provide innovative solutions for high added-value thermoplastic components to all demanding businesses. We make overmoulded thermoplastic components and overmould all types of inserts cut in metal, plastic, glass, copper alloys, brass, etc.
